OL,7,FThere are currently 126 Labour MPs who
OL,8,Fhave signed the amendment, along with
OL,9,F36 MPs from other parties. MPs will
OL,10,Fvote on the plans on Tuesday July 1.
OL,12,FIs your MP part of the group of 126
OL,13,FLabour backbenchers rebelling against
OL,14,Fthe government? Type their first name
OL,15,For surname (not their full name
OL,16,Ftogether), or your constituency in the
OL,17,Fsearch bar below to find out:
OL,19,F72 of the 126 Labour MPs who have
OL,20,Fsigned the amendment are new MPs who
OL,21,Fwere elected at the election last July.
