OL,7,FThere are also understood to be a
OL,8,Fnumber of other MPs who are concerned
OL,9,Fabout the cuts but haven't currently
OL,10,Fput their names to the amendment.
OL,12,FDespite days of resisting calls to
OL,13,Fchange course and insisting they will
OL,14,Fpress ahead - on Thursday the
OL,15,Fgovernment changed their tone,
OL,16,Findicating they are looking at
OL,17,Fconcessions through "conversations"
OL,18,Fwith rebels.
