OL,7,FThe plans restrict eligibility for
OL,8,Fpersonal independence payment (Pip),
OL,9,Fthe main disability payment in
OL,10,FEngland, and limit the sickness-
OL,11,Frelated element of universal credit.
OL,12,FThe government hopes the changes will
OL,13,Fget more people back into work and
OL,14,Fsave up to #5 billion a year.
